sequenceDiagram
    participant CS as CrawlSession
    participant PR as PluginRunner
    participant ST as stealthPlugin
    participant CC as cookieConsentPlugin
    participant AS as autoScrollPlugin
    participant DE as domExpansionPlugin
    participant CO as cssOverridePlugin
    participant ER as ExtractionRunner
    participant SS as screenshotPlugin

    Note over CS: requestHandler fires per URL

    CS->>PR: runHook('beforeNavigate', ctx)
    PR->>ST: hooks.beforeNavigate(ctx)
    Note right of ST: Inject stealth scripts<br/>Hide webdriver flag
    ST-->>PR: { enabled, patches }
    PR->>CO: hooks.beforeNavigate(ctx)
    Note right of CO: Setup route blocking<br/>for widget domains
    CO-->>PR: { blocked_domains }

    CS->>CS: page.goto(url)

    CS->>PR: runHook('afterNavigate', ctx)
    PR->>CC: hooks.afterNavigate(ctx)
    Note right of CC: Autoconsent CMP (95%+)<br/>Fallback selector clicks<br/>Settle delay
    CC-->>PR: { autoconsentMatched, fallbackClicked }

    CS->>PR: runHook('onInteract', ctx)
    PR->>AS: hooks.onInteract(ctx)
    Note right of AS: Jump or incremental scroll<br/>Lazy content trigger<br/>Stability detection
    AS-->>PR: { strategy, passes }
    PR->>DE: hooks.onInteract(ctx)
    Note right of DE: Click expand buttons<br/>Reveal collapsed sections<br/>maxClicks cap
    DE-->>PR: { found, clicked }
    PR->>CO: hooks.onInteract(ctx)
    Note right of CO: CSS inject: reveal hidden<br/>Remove fixed/sticky
    CO-->>PR: { hidden_before, hidden_after }

    Note over CS,ER: Context deep-frozen before extraction

    CS->>ER: runExtractions(frozenCtx)
    ER->>SS: onExtract(frozenCtx)
    Note right of SS: Selector crops (up to 12)<br/>Full-page screenshot<br/>Size-bounded captures
    SS-->>ER: { screenshots: [...] }

    Note over ER: Return aggregated extractions

    CS->>PR: runHook('onComplete', ctx)
    Note over CS: Record to frontier DB<br/>Write video manifest
